					<op:txt>
						<sc:para xml:space="preserve">
			 Soient <sc:textLeaf role="mathtex">a</sc:textLeaf> et <sc:textLeaf role="mathtex">b</sc:textLeaf> deux réels. On a <sc:textLeaf role="mathtex">\sin(a+b)-\sin(a-b)</sc:textLeaf> égal à</sc:para>
